(399, 'studenttrail02', '                                                                                                                <div><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 24px;\">Why Join the Transdisciplinary Education Expedition?</h2></div><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><li><strong>To Embrace Future Skills:</strong> In todays ever-changing world, higher education isnt just about getting a job – its your ticket to gaining skills for a brighter future. Were talking leadership, innovation, and problem-solving skills. You might have felt that traditional education falls short, and that is where we step in. Dive into the next steps to discover how we can empower you for a meaningful life and a successful career.</li><li><strong>To Build a Better Future as a Change-Maker in Education:</strong> The cracks in societal, ecological, and planetary well-being are calling for a change in education. Wicked problems demand a co-creative, multidisciplinary approach. Education needs to produce change-makers who can address evolving challenges. Get ready to make an impact.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\">Links:</h2><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 20px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><li>Future Thinking</li><li>Holism</li><li>Inner Development Goals</li><li>Systemic Change</li></ul>                                                                                                  ', 1, '8', 3),
